109-chinese-045", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-109-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，「稚子數請所出」句中「數請所出」的涵義最可能是下列何者？", "options": ["再三懇請父親出來宴客", "多次詢問小室命名由來", "屢次延請賓客前往休憩", "頻頻敦請姻賓離室用餐"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-109-chinese-passage-45", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ed74d9cea4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "64e8d2b7d3a1", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 45, "raw_text": "45. 根據本文，「稚子數請所出」句中「數請所出」的涵義最可能是下列何者？\n    (A)再三懇請父親出來宴客\n    (B)多次詢問小室命名由來\n    (C)屢次延請賓客前往休憩\n    (D)頻頻敦請姻賓離室用餐\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-109-chinese-046", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-109-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，雅志堂後名為「更衣」的小室，其主要用途與現代哪一種場所最\n接近？", "options": ["兒童遊戲場", "商場試衣間", "婚禮宴會廳", "賓客休息室"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-109-chinese-passage-45", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ed74d9cea4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "64e8d2b7d3a1", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 46, "raw_text": "46. 根據本文，雅志堂後名為「更衣」的小室，其主要用途與現代哪一種場所最\n    接近？\n    (A)兒童遊戲場\n    (B)商場試衣間\n    (C)婚禮宴會廳\n    (D)賓客休息室\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-109-chinese-047", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-109-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "下列文句「」中的字，何者意義說明正確？         ", "options": ["「孰」能磨之：難道                1.然：如此", "朝夕相與「俱」：具備            